	//  Outfit DNA is an object that contains the outfit data that needed to
	//  create the player oufit anywhere remotly. It is player outfit assets
	//  in transfered structure ( aka like .toJSON() ).
	//
	//  .toDNA(); .fromDNA(dna); Usage:
